flowchart TD
    A([User submits credentials]) --> B{Credentials valid?}
    B -- No --> C([Return 401 login error])
    B -- Yes --> D[Create session record in store]
    D --> E[Generate random session ID]
    E --> F[Set-Cookie: session_id=XXXX HttpOnly Secure SameSite]
    F --> G([User receives session cookie])

    G --> H([Browser sends request with cookie])
    H --> I{Session ID in store?}
    I -- Not found --> J([Redirect to login])
    I -- Found --> K{Session expired?}
    K -- Yes --> L[Delete session record]
    L --> J
    K -- No --> M[Load user data from session]
    M --> N([Return protected resource])

    N --> O([User clicks logout])
    O --> P[Delete session record from store]
    P --> Q[Clear session cookie]
    Q --> J
